
If you want to work with Playwright locators on chromium;

First open CMD and navigate to project folder

Then execute following commands;

1- USAGE:
    mvn exec:java -e -Dexec.mainClass=com.microsoft.playwright.CLI

2- Install ALL browsers and dependencies
    mvn exec:java -e -Dexec.mainClass=com.microsoft.playwright.CLI -Dexec.args="install"

3- Start playwright and CODE GENERATOR-> Open a browser and navigate to "wikipedia.org"
    mvn exec:java -e -Dexec.mainClass=com.microsoft.playwright.CLI -Dexec.args="codegen wikipedia.org"